  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 31e2412c87638a942b571fad5d879d57, type: 3}
  m_Name: ClassroomLesson_ForcedPlayerMovement_FoR_Sharp
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ClassroomTitle: 
  LessonSteps:
  - m_DialogueString: Welcome back to the classroom. You have just experienced the
      second variant of Forced Movement.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bfd070a869b6c3b4cbdd73c3d6de06ca, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: How would you describe the experience you just had? Compare
      it with the first experience. What difference have you noticed or felt?
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bfd070a869b6c3b4cbdd73c3d6de06ca, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: In this set up, the frame of reference remains the same. However,
      the turns in the maps are sharper, causing a higher level of vection.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f2951fe0fbd72614190ed69e7efeb1bc, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: As mentioned before, sharper turns result in our surrounding
      moving at a higher speed.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f2951fe0fbd72614190ed69e7efeb1bc, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "Hence, our visual stimulus tells our brain that we are moving
      much faster compared to the information relayed from our vestibular system,
      indicating that we are almost stationary. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f2951fe0fbd72614190ed69e7efeb1bc, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'Hence, this significant mismatch throws us off balance, making
      us feel nauseous. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f92cba5a1bfd64e4083c020467919e66, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'In the next experience, you will ride through the same map,
      but with a different setting implemented. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6f13ccda2f65ea04c9ea4559772ef214, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'Whenever you are ready, proceed to the door on your left. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6f13ccda2f65ea04c9ea4559772ef214, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
